msgid ""
"Migrate a config server to a new system while keeping the same hostname. "
"This procedure requires changing the DNS entry to point to the new system."
msgstr ""
"保持域名不变的情况下如何迁移配置服务器到一个信息的系统.需要修改DNS条目使得新"
